": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/a0edd35cf6cbcb81d95afcd8f8c9d2ac539d0314/libgfortran%2FChangeLog", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/libgfortran%2FChangeLog?ref=a0edd35cf6cbcb81d95afcd8f8c9d2ac539d0314", "patch": "@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@\n+2012-12-21  Thomas Koenig  <tkoenig@gcc.gnu.org>\n+\n+\tPR libfortran/30162\n+\t* io/unix.c (raw_tell):  If the lseek is done on a\n+\tnon-seekable file, return 0.\n+\n 2012-12-20  Janus Weil  <janus@gcc.gnu.org>\n \n \tPR fortran/36044"}, {"sha": "e690aec77a562f17438624c878e31034f6486724", "filename": "libgfortran/io/unix.c", "status": "modified", "additions": 9, "deletions": 1, "changes": 10, "blob_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/blob/a0edd35cf6cbcb81d95afcd8f8c9d2ac539d0314/libgfortran%2Fio%2Funix.c", "raw_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/a0edd35cf6cbcb81d95afcd8f8c9d2ac539d0314/libgfortran%2Fio%2Funix.c", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/libgfortran%2Fio%2Funix.c?ref=a0edd35cf6cbcb81d95afcd8f8c9d2ac539d0314", "patch": "@@ -344,7 +344,15 @@ raw_seek (unix_stream * s, gfc_offset offset, int whence)\n static gfc_offset\n raw_tell (unix_stream * s)\n {\n-  return lseek (s->fd, 0, SEEK_CUR);\n+  gfc_offset x;\n+  x = lseek (s->fd, 0, SEEK_CUR);\n+\n+  /* Non-seekable files should always be assumed to be at\n+     current position.  */\n+  if (x == -1 && errno == ESPIPE)\n+    x = 0;\n+\n+  return x;\n }\n \n static gfc_offset"}]}